data.description: This beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home with a den that could be converted in to a 4th bedroom is a must see in Mountain Falls. It has a large living room that opens to the kitchen. The backyard is it's own little oasis with a covered patio and artificial grass, so nothing to mow. The home has mature landscaping, front and back yard.. Mountain falls has so much to offer, including a pool, spa, fitness center, club house and restaurant. Beautifully maintained lush golf course. Seller will consider selling furnishing with the home. This property has an assumable VA loan at 3.2% . You do not need to be a veteran to assume this loan.  $355,000 remains on the loan. Current payments are at $1876.00 per month
